text: Realitatea Plus (meaning "The Reality Plus") is an all-news channel launched on 16 January 2015 that took the place of Realitatea TV. Its owners are Romanian politician Cozmin Guşă and businessman Maricel Păcuraru. ==History== Realitatea Plus was launched on 16 January 2015. Realitatea Plus replacing the defunct all-news channel Realitatea TV. == Other websites == * Official Site Category:Television channels in Romania
